---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { pageMetadata } from "../lib/site";

export const prerender = true;
---

<BaseLayout
    title={pageMetadata.phases.title}
    description={pageMetadata.phases.description}
    canonical={pageMetadata.phases.canonical}
    noindex={pageMetadata.phases.noindex}
>
    <main class="w-full flex-1 bg-csp-background text-csp-black">
        
        <section class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 items-stretch overflow-hidden">
            
            <div class="absolute -left-20 top-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-csp-primary/5 blur-3xl -z-10"></div>

            <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center py-16 lg:py-24 lg:pr-12 relative z-10">
                <h1 class="font-display text-[2.5rem] md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-[1.1] text-csp-black mb-8">
                    Premios y reconocimientos
                </h1>
                
                <div class="inline-flex items-start gap-4 bg-[#f4f5f8] border-l-4 border-csp-primary p-5 lg:p-6 rounded-r-2xl max-w-lg shadow-sm">
                    <div class="bg-csp-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-csp-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                        <p class="font-display font-bold text-csp-black text-xl lg:text-2xl">Por anunciar</p>
                        <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-black/60 font-inter leading-relaxed">
                            Estamos preparando sorpresas increíbles para los equipos ganadores de ambas categorías. ¡Mantente atento a nuestras redes!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            
            <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 lg:col-span-5 relative min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-full w-auto -mx-4 sm:-mx-6 lg:mx-0">
                <img 
                    src="/registerPhotos/premiacion.png" 
                    alt="Personas trabajando" 
                    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-left lg:object-left foto-premios" 
                />
            </div>
            
        </section>
        
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col">
            
            <section class="relative w-full bg-[#f4f5f8] pt-24 pb-8 lg:pb-12 overflow-hidden">
                
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
                    <div class="w-20 md:w-48 lg:w-64 h-32 md:h-64 lg:h-80 bg-csp-primary rounded-br-[100%]"></div>
                    <div class="absolute top-20 md:top-44 left-0 w-6 md:w-10 h-12 md:h-20 bg-[#0BAA9F] rounded-r-full border-t-[8px] md:border-t-[12px] border-b-[8px] md:border-b-[12px] border-[#f4f5f8]"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 z-0 pointer-events-none flex justify-end transform scale-50 lg:scale-100 origin-top-right">
                    <div class="absolute top-10 right-8 w-16 h-16 bg-csp-primary rounded-tl-full opacity-80"></div>
                    <div class="mt-20 w-32 h-64 border-[16px] border-csp-primary/20 rounded-l-full translate-x-12"></div>
                    <div class="absolute top-36 right-0 w-16 h-32 bg-csp-primary rounded-l-full"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-4">
                    
                    <div class="text-center mb-16 relative z-20">
                        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3 text-csp-black">
                            Fases de la competencia
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-[1.05rem] text-[#6b629b] font-inter">
                            La Copa Salvadoreña de Programación consta de dos fases:
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_15px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 w-full relative">
                        
                        <div class="p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <h3 class="font-display text-[1.75rem] md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-csp-black">Fase en línea</h3>
                            <h4 class="font-display text-xl md:text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#6b629b]">Lugar: Plataforma virtual</h4>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-[0.95rem] text-black/80 font-inter leading-relaxed">
                                <p>En esta fase, los equipos competirán por un puesto en la fase presencial resolviendo 6 problemas de forma remota.</p>
                                <p>Los mejores equipos avanzarán a la fase presencial. Pueden participar TODOS los equipos que deseen de una misma institución. En esta fase, no hay límite de participación.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 font-poppins mt-auto">
                                
                                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f4f5f8] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                    <div class="bg-csp-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl text-csp-primary shrink-0">
                                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                                            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
                                            <path d="M8 14h.01M12 14h.01M16 14h.01M8 18h.01M12 18h.01M16 18h.01"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold text-csp-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-0.5">Fecha</span>
                                        <span class="font-bold text-csp-black text-[0.95rem]">1 y 2 de agosto del 2026</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f4f5f8] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                    <div class="bg-csp-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl text-csp-primary shrink-0">
                                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                                            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold text-csp-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-0.5">Horario</span>
                                        <span class="font-bold text-csp-black text-[0.95rem]">8:00 am del sábado - 11:59 pm del domingo</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-full">
                            <img src="/index/colegios.webp" alt="Equipo programando en línea" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center" />
                        </div>
                    </article>

                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="relative w-full bg-csp-primary pt-8 lg:pt-12 pb-16 lg:pb-24 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-4">
                    
                    <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_15px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 w-full relative">
                        
                        <div class="relative min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-full order-last lg:order-first">
                            <img src="/index/universidades.webp" alt="Laboratorios ESEN" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center" />
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <h3 class="font-display text-[1.75rem] md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-csp-black">Fases presenciales</h3>
                            <h4 class="font-display text-xl md:text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#6b629b]">Lugar: Campus ESEN</h4>
                            
                            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-[0.95rem] text-black/80 font-inter leading-relaxed">
                                <p>Los equipos resolverán 6 problemas de programación en un tiempo máximo de 4 horas directamente desde los laboratorios de informática de la ESEN.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 font-poppins mt-auto">
                                <div class="w-full flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f4f5f8] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                    <div class="bg-csp-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl text-csp-primary shrink-0 self-start sm:self-center">
                                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                                            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
                                            <path d="M8 14h.01M12 14h.01M16 14h.01M8 18h.01M12 18h.01M16 18h.01"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
                                        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold text-csp-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Fechas por categoría</span>
                                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-1 sm:gap-6">
                                            <span class="font-bold text-csp-black text-[0.95rem]">Colegios: 15 de agosto</span>
                                            <span class="font-bold text-csp-black text-[0.95rem]">Universidades: 5 de septiembre</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#f4f5f8] p-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                    <div class="bg-csp-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl text-csp-primary shrink-0">
                                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                                            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold text-csp-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-0.5">Horario</span>
                                        <span class="font-bold text-csp-black text-[0.95rem]">8:00 am</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </article>

                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <style>
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .font-inter {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        .font-display {
            font-family: var(--font-display), 'Poppins', system-ui, sans-serif;
        }
        
        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .foto-premios {
                -o-object-position: 15% center;
                object-position: 15% center;
                -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, transparent 10%, black 50%);
                mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, transparent 10%, black 50%);
            }
        }
    </style>
</BaseLayout>